sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant HotCache as Hot Cache<br>(boot files)
    participant RLM as rlm-factory / rlm-search<br>(query_cache.py)
    participant VDB as vector-db / vector-db-agent<br>(query.py)
    participant Grep as Grep / rg<br>(exact search)
    participant Deep as Deep Storage<br>(domain / design / governance)

    Note over Agent, HotCache: Tier 1 -- Always loaded at boot (~200 lines)

    Agent->>HotCache: "What is my current task?"
    HotCache-->>Agent: primer + digest + contract + snapshot

    alt Hot Cache sufficient (~90% of queries)
        Agent->>Agent: Proceed with full context
    else Hot Cache miss -- need on-demand lookup
        Note over Agent, RLM: Phase 1 -- RLM Summary Ledger (Table of Contents)
        Note right of Agent: Pre-work: each file read ONCE,<br>summarized ONCE, cached forever.<br>O(1) keyword substring search.

        Agent->>RLM: query_cache.py --profile plugins "vector search"
        RLM-->>Agent: 1-sentence dense summary + file path

        alt Phase 1 sufficient -- summary answers the question
            Agent->>Agent: Proceed with high-level understanding
        else Phase 1 miss -- need exact content
            Note over Agent, VDB: Phase 2 -- Vector Store Semantic Search (Back-of-Book Index)
            Agent->>VDB: query.py "nearest-neighbor embedding search"
            VDB-->>Agent: Ranked parent chunks + RLM Super-RAG context injected

            alt Phase 2 sufficient -- chunk contains the answer
                Agent->>Agent: Deep analysis on returned chunks
            else Phase 2 miss -- need exact line or symbol
                Note over Agent, Grep: Phase 3 -- Grep / Exact Search (Ctrl+F)
                Agent->>Grep: rg "symbol" ../../ --type py
                Grep->>Deep: Search scoped to paths from Phase 1 or 2
                Deep-->>Grep: Exact matching lines + line numbers
                Grep-->>Agent: Precise file location
                Agent->>Agent: Read targeted section only
            end
        end
    end
